data.description: Amazing opportunity! This cozy 2 bedroom bungalow rests on a large corner lot in Lakeside, with a fully fenced in backyard and the perfect deck for evening barbecues! Newly repainted, and with updated flooring, kitchen, warm bright cozy spaces, low utilities, and newer mechanicals, there is nothing to do but move in and relax! With plenty of off street parking and lots of space for storage in the sheds, you can take your time to plan your perfect garage! Within minutes of the Lakewalk/Lester trails including hiking, golf, and cross -country, and just 10-15 minutes from Downtown, the Colleges, Craft and Mall Districts. All at a price that is cheaper than rent! Don't wait to come see your new home!
